{"tid":1394463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 何妖對肥奶強烈譴責活塞行動","createTime":"2019-08-01T12:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T10:33:13.000Z","uid":232014,"like":11,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"812c1232a61fa5fb53004003dd6c2ce81e33c431","tid":1394463,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:02:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>對唔住！我係一半標題黨！<br />\n比返張肥妖你睇</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U3pDHe2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU3pDHe2.png&h=2f92a4f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呃左大家入黎既活塞行動其實係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>805「兩山一景」塞鐵！！</strong></span></span><br />\n但係呢個都係要各打工仔出於<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自發性既罷工！</span></span><br />\n唔好唔記得，香港人好少會肯同你自發罷工<br />\n我自己身邊已經有好多人打算<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>比人強迫有得罷先罷</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算你咁好彩身邊既人都想罷工<br />\n我求下你都一定要幫下呢啲人<br />\n等佢地果日下晝可以有藉口去集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月5號 7:30<br />\n荔景<br />\n鑽石山<br />\n炮台山</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/mstopthem\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmstopthem&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEa9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=0f5e328b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/mstopthem</a><br />\n<br />\n塞返係市區 等啲人唔駛出到商業區<br />\n去返自己區集會都簡單啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到有post話8月5號千祈唔好塞鐵你就知道<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對家好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">見到730靜係塞調景嶺都已經咁大影響，對家而家驚到係咁叫人咪塞</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>而家仲要塞3個站<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信黎緊會有更多3毛post叫人唔好塞鐵</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再睇下塞鐵效果你就知道點解佢地咁驚你塞鐵<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pJQfKu2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpJQfKu2.png&h=41a79cdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">零成本得黎，影響大，阻嚇唔到示威者，仲要可以對香港經濟做到一定既影響！</span></span><br />\n大家為左前線唔駛再食催淚彈，可唔可以大家都出黎幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">少你一個都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/mstopthem\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmstopthem&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEa9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=0f5e328b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/mstopthem</a>"},{"pid":"aed9101123ecd3d87997a362bdeb0b74718d4c8c","tid":1394463,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:02:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c483edcb7c065615eeb3f7d573baa860ff0a1a5","tid":1394463,"uid":232014,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ao8tj32.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAo8tj32.png&h=9759f80f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bfb3d164833b1bab5630f0474f5922c039d08b0d","tid":1394463,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:03:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"989127b73ef92d7a097c74190c57f952c05cd2e3","tid":1394463,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/